parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the plastic timing chain tensioner can cause the timing chain to break, leading to engine failure, which can result in accidents, loss of property, or even loss of life.
symptoms: oil sludge build-up in the oil pan

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or fail to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle fails to shift into gear
the vehicle lunges forward when attempting to stop
the vehicle feels like it's losing power while driving at highway speeds
the accelerator pedal is applied but the vehicle fails to move
the vehicle drives very slowly and sluggishly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of serious injury or fatality to the occupants.
